ike space weather conditions. If the radio telescopes measure a\nrelative low radio emission signal with small variability from an exoplanet,\nthat may indicate favorable exoplanet habitability conditions with respect to\nthe space weather states considered and the intrinsic magnetic field of the\nexoplanet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2023 06:59:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-19"}
