ics. In addition, integration is an important part of any temporal\ntask, so the proposed Input-Weighted Threshold Adaptation (IWTA) mechanism may\nhave implications well beyond control tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2023 07:21:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-19"}
