easible route to mass production of 3C-SiC crystals,offering new\nopportunities to develop power electronic devices potentially with better\nperformances than those based on 4H-SiC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2023 15:38:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-19"}
